data.name: label21.Text
data.value: This software has not had formal testing applied to it. Care should be taken when using this software for accuracy. Although the software has not had major errors for some time there still may be hidden bugs. If a bug has been found please send relevant files and screenshots to logicnavigator@gmail.com. This version is free to use and distribute. There is no warranty or support associated with this software however the developer is generally available to assist with technical issues.
